I cannot believe that. I mean, look at the disadvantages of rains:
<br />
- damage over time, as opposed to the instant nukes.
<br />
- target must remain stationary.
<br />
- cannot be used around mezed mobs.
<br />
- limited in the number of mobs it can hit / number of waves that can hit several mobs.
<br />
- long recast times.
<br />
- evocation based.
<br />
- not focused by improved damage focus items.
<br />

<br />
